The '''lifeblood cleaver''' was a large battle axe that was used by the more [[Blood/Legends|bloodthirsty]] [[Sayormi]] warriors of the [[Kkowir Forest/Legends|Kkowir Forest]] on the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. It was named for its ability to spill the blood of even the fiercest foe.

